'''Wartaki''' was the name of an island continent on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]].

It was most likely a large part of the [[Wartaki Islands/Legends|Wartaki Islands]]. The dialect [[Xaczik/Legends|Xaczik]], a difficult dialect, was developed on Wartaki to confuse and/or fool the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]]' [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] masters in the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

